data.value: Since its foundation in 1998, Hope Microelectronics Ltd has become one of the most successful designers and manufacturers in digital sensor, RF IC, RF discrete devices and related application solutions. We have co-operated technically with world-famous ASIC design companies in USA and Germany, and from these countries we introduced advanced packaging and testing lines and sophisticated calibration instruments so as to guarantee products' high quality and stability. We are able to develop and design customized RF and digital sensor chips. With keeping pace with international advanced mangement and owning a strong team of experienced engineers, we have independently developed digital sensor chips and its packaging and calibration technology with our own intellectual property. By offering our customers software application platforms and supporting related hardware designs on RF and digital sensor. We can be able to provide one-stop produce solutions to dramatically shorten customers' development period reducing customers' purchasing cost. Our company has gained a good reputaion in the market for low cost, fast delivery and all-round after-sales service. Hope's products have been widely accepted by reputable global companies and extensively being used in diverse fields such as wireless anti-theft alarm system, wireless sensor, household automation, wireless high-speed data acquisition system, wireless toy, temperature & humidity control system, intruments and meters, pressure measurement and control system, mobile altimeter/barometer system, multi-functional sports watches, weather forecast system, etc.
